&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has become available for a clinical support worker to come and join our team in eye clinic. We are a very busy outpatients department with the patient at the heart of all we do. Candidates need to be enthusiastic, hard working, flexible and have a keen interest in ophthalmology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will support candidates with further training if needed within ophthalmology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion or any information about this role please contact Sister Leona Mercer or Sister Leah Butterfield on 01516785111 ext 2896 or on the following email&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;leona.battrimmercer@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;leah.butterfield@nhs.net for any queries or an informal visit.&lt;/p&gt;
